    <note>Chao(2) Zongque [8001] Zhongyan's [7119] father, Buzhi's [13] great grandfather. His great grandson Zaizhi's [3020] grandfather-in-law was Wei(5) Guan [1945]. Buzhi was the son of the sister of Gao(1) Dan's [924] wife, Wang(2) Shi. Zongque's great grandson, Yongzhi [3028], was Lu(5) Shimin's [1287] son-in-law. Chao(2) Zongque was the uncle or father of Wang(2) Han's [1810] son-in-law, Chao(2) Zhongwei [3014]. According to Wang Gui's funerary inscription for Zongyue's son, Zhongyan, Zongyue's wife was Wang(2) Gui's [1845] aunt and, therefore, Wang Zhi(5)'s [1783] daughter. CBD, 3, 1951-2.[Kinship with Zhongyuan and Zhonghui is not yet checked. 與晁仲淵、晁仲徽的親戚關係未考。]</note>
